user-data-dir/<distro>/
Base #cloud-config / autoinstall templates per Ubuntu release
packages-dir/, bootcmd-dir/, mounts-dir/, runcmd-dir/, apt-dir/
Role-specific slices (e.g. docker, jenkins, gluster, general)
